    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Add a disclaimer\/terms\/warnings about post\/page\/custom post type on top, bottom of content as well as inside post content<\/p>\n<h4>Features<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Disclaimer on Post\/Page or Custom Post Type<\/li>\n<li>Customized Options<\/li>\n<li>Custom CSS Option<\/li>\n<li>Individual Post\/Page or Custom Post Type Options<\/li>\n<li>Font Awesome Icons<\/li>\n<li>Use with Shortcode<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<h4>Automatic Installation<\/h4>\n<p>Login to your WordPress dashboard and navigate to the Plugins menu, and click &#8220;Add New&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>In the search input type &#8220;WP Post Disclaimer&#8221; then hit enter. Once you have found a plugin, you can view details about plugin and you can install it by click &#8220;Install Now&#8221; and WordPress will take it from there.<\/p>\n<h4>Manual Installation<\/h4>\n<p>Download &#8220;WP Post Disclaimer&#8221; plugin and upload it to your server via your FTP. The WordPress codex contains <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/article\/managing-plugins\/#manual-plugin-installation\" rel=\"ugc\">instructions on how to doing this here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Once installation done, then go to Dashboard &gt; Settings &gt; WP Post Disclaimer and then set up all the options as per your need and enjoy the plugin!<\/p>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='where%20can%20i%20find%20wp%20post%20disclaimer%20global%20settings%3F'>\nWhere can I find WP Post Disclaimer Global Settings?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can find them under Dashboard &gt; Settings &gt; WP Post Disclaimer<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='where%20can%20i%20find%20individual%20wp%20post%20disclaimer%20settings%3F'>\nWhere can I find individual WP Post Disclaimer Settings?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can find them under post edit screen &gt; WP Post Disclaimer<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>Version 1.0.4 &#8211; 09-02-2024<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Content escaping html tags<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 &#8211; 03-02-2024<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Cross Site Scripting issue in shortcode<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2 &#8211; 15-03-2021<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add &#8211; Language .pot file<\/li>\n<li>Add &#8211; WPML config file<\/li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Strip slashes for quotes in disclaimer content.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; 06-05-2020<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Metabox icon update issue<\/li>\n<li>Add &#8211; &#8220;None&#8221; Option for icon to hide Icon<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 &#8211; 10-01-2020<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release *<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
